Description_lang: When Lifebloom blooms, up to $s1 targets within your Efflorescence are healed for $392329s1.

description_blz.en_US: When Lifebloom blooms, up to 3 targets within your Efflorescence are healed for 4,303.
description_blz.es_MX: Cuando Flor de vida florece, un máximo de 3 objetivos dentro de tu Floración reciben una sanación de 4,303 p.
description_blz.pt_BR: Quando Brotar da Vida floresce, cura 4.303 pontos de vida de até 3 alvos dentro da sua Eflorescência.
description_blz.de_DE: Wenn 'Blühendes Leben' aufblüht, werden bis zu 3 Ziele im Effektbereich von Eurem 'Erblühen' um 4.303 Gesundheit geheilt.
description_blz.en_GB: When Lifebloom blooms, up to 3 targets within your Efflorescence are healed for 4,303.

description_blz.ko_KR: 피어나는 생명이 만개하면 자신의 꽃피우기의 범위 내에 있는 최대 3명의 대상을 4,303만큼 치유합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 生命之花開花時，使生命綻放範圍內最多3名目標恢復4,303點生命力。
description_blz.zh_CN: 生命绽放进行最终绽放时，可以治疗最多3名拥有你的百花齐放效果的目标，使其恢复4,303点生命值。
